---
layout: base.njk
title: "Areas Covered: Derby, Bakewell, Matlock, East & West Midlands"
description: "Professional removals serving Derby, Bakewell, Matlock, Chesterfield, Nottingham, Birmingham, Leicester and beyond since 1988."
keywords: "removals Derby, removals Bakewell, removals Matlock, removals Chesterfield, removals east midlands, removals west midlands"
ogImage: "/images/business/van.jpg"
---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 pt-52 pb-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#071059]">Areas We Cover</h1>

    <p class="text-lg mb-8">
      Derbyshire Removals provides professional moving services across the East and West Midlands.
      With local expertise in key locations, we ensure a smooth and efficient moving experience
      wherever you're relocating to or from.
    </p>

    {# Only link additional areas if you actually have a /locations/... page for them #}
    {% set additionalAreaLinks = {
      "Leicester": "/locations/leicester/",
      "Sheffield": "/locations/sheffield/",
      "Birmingham": "/locations/birmingham/"
    } %}

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      {% for location in locations.primaryLocations %}
        <section class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="h-5 w-5 text-[#071059] mr-2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
            </svg>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">
              <a href="{{ location.link }}" class="text-[#071059] underline underline-offset-2">
                Removals in {{ location.name }}
              </a>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">{{ location.description }}</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">House removals, office moves, packing and storage.</p>

          <a href="{{ location.link }}" class="text-[#071059] font-medium">
            Learn more â†’
          </a>
        </section>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">Additional Coverage Areas</h2>

      <p class="mb-6">
        Beyond our primary service locations, we also offer removal services to many other areas including:
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {% for areaName in locations.additionalAreas %}
          {% set areaLink = additionalAreaLinks[areaName] %}
          <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-2">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="h-4 w-4 text-[#071059] mr-2" aria-hidden="true">
                <path d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
              </svg>

              <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">
                {% if areaLink %}
                  <a href="{{ areaLink }}" class="underline underline-offset-2">
                    Removals in {{ areaName }}
                  </a>
                {% else %}
                  Removals in {{ areaName }}
                {% endif %}
              </h2>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-600">House removals, office moves, packing and storage.</p>
          </section>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="mb-4">Don't see your location listed? We likely still cover it!</p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors"
        >
          Contact Us to Confirm
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

